{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"355328e222","title":"庐山会议讨论问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f56893b16f","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"355328e222"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"86760f43d8","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指当时正在庐山召开的中共中央政治局扩大会议。"},{"id":"b71492fca3","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1959年6月29日，毛泽东在同各协作区主任座谈时，提出了在庐山会议上准备讨论的若于问题。7月2日，中共中央政治局常委开会确定为十八个问题，印发庐山会议各同志。7月3日，毛泽东对这个提纲又作了修改，即本篇一。本篇题目也是毛泽东在这次修改时定的。"},{"id":"69c1fbef42","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是当时准备为县、社干部编印的三本书。"},{"id":"dbe98d0399","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央和国务院自1957年以来为改进财经工作的管理体制而下放的人、工、财、商四天管理权限。"},{"id":"b92eb63dd4","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"970bd2f148","type":"title","text":"庐山会议讨论问题？","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"86760f43d8","type":"paragraph","text":"一、读书。高级干部读《政治经济学教科书》第三版下册。读者范围，由中央委员到县委书记，都要读。县级主要干部，首先是第一书记，另读三本书：“好人好事”一本、“环人环事”一本、中央的政策和工作方法的文件一本。以三本书不超过十万字，七天能够读完。然后讨论三个星期，共学一个月。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"b71492fca3","type":"paragraph","text":"每年轮训县社干部。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"69c1fbef42","type":"paragraph","text":"二、形势。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"dbe98d0399","type":"paragraph","text":"三、今年的任务。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"b92eb63dd4","type":"paragraph","text":"四、明年的任务。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"184a07a555","type":"paragraph","text":"五、四年的任务。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"3ae719c039","type":"paragraph","text":"六、宣传问题。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"8636c99a16","type":"paragraph","text":"七、综合平衡问题。工业和农业中都有。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"20d3ad2069","type":"paragraph","text":"八、群众路线问题。工业和农业中的。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"07e4942d7d","type":"paragraph","text":"九、建立和加强工业企业的各项管理制度和提高工业产品的质量问题。这两个问题，都是极大的问题，立即抓起，一年完成，某些两年完成。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"65399d6bda","type":"paragraph","text":"十、体制问题。即人权、工权、财权、商权问题。四大下放权力”，现要收回，由中央、省市区党委两级控制，反对无政府主义","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"4a3ab23911","type":"paragraph","text":"十一、协作区关系问题。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"d69a3bd994","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、公社食堂问题。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"b50e561262","type":"paragraph","text":"十三、学会过日子问题。富日子当穷日子过，立于不败之地。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"627bbdc7c9","type":"paragraph","text":"十四、三定政策。粮食定产、定购、定销，三年不变。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"fda450db1f","type":"paragraph","text":"十五、农村初级市场的恢复问题","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"10046ba2ef","type":"paragraph","text":"十六、使生产小队成为半基本核算单位。（即要它负担一部分发工资的任务。允许生产小队之间，由于生产和经营的好环，可以在工资、口粮、肉食上有差别。）","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"cbccf6a9f0","type":"paragraph","text":"十七、农村党团基层组织的领导作用问题","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"68d074bb78","type":"paragraph","text":"十八、团结问题。中央至县委。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"526020fe87","type":"paragraph","text":"十九、国际问题尚昆”","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"b110cf5e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"此件再印，换发，原发件收回。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"90baaced51","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"ffb45deae0","type":"paragraph","text":"七月三日一时半","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"},{"id":"aacd383702","type":"paragraph","text":"1959年7月2日至8月16日，中共中央政治局扩大会议和中共八届八中全会先后在庐山举行。图为毛泽东、刘少奇、周恩来等在庐山会议上。","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222"}],"page":{"id":"518dd7b16d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"355328e222","start":161,"end":163}}}},"__N_SSG":true}